WEBVTT

00:00:01.750 --> 00:00:03.810
{\an9}Special Week

00:00:03.810 --> 00:00:08.270
I'm sure your debut race will work out
fine if you train hard for a week.

00:00:08.480 --> 00:00:10.940
"Work out fine"? You should
take this more seriously!

00:00:08.590 --> 00:00:12.260
{\an7}Daiwa Scarlet

00:00:08.590 --> 00:00:12.260
{\an8}Gold Ship

00:00:08.590 --> 00:00:12.260
{\an9}Vodka

00:00:10.940 --> 00:00:13.240
Yeah, take this a bit more seriously!

00:00:16.230 --> 00:00:17.700
It's time to eat.

00:00:17.700 --> 00:00:19.070
Clean up for us.

00:00:19.070 --> 00:00:19.870
Hold up!

00:00:19.870 --> 00:00:22.160
We're going, too!

00:00:23.770 --> 00:00:27.380
Anyway, it'll be nice working with you.

00:00:32.250 --> 00:00:33.080
Um…

00:00:33.080 --> 00:00:35.930
Were you nervous about your debut match?

00:00:35.930 --> 00:00:37.960
Not really.

00:00:35.950 --> 00:00:38.660
{\an9}Silence Suzuka

00:00:37.960 --> 00:00:39.800
Y-You weren't, huh?

00:00:39.800 --> 00:00:43.060
<i>She's on a completely different level.</i>

00:00:43.060 --> 00:00:46.810
The only thing I can do
is run. That's why.

00:00:47.380 --> 00:00:49.400
<i>She's so cool!</i>

00:00:49.400 --> 00:00:52.200
Um, I totally look up to you.

00:00:52.200 --> 00:00:55.130
I'm really happy to be
on the same team as you.

00:00:57.300 --> 00:00:58.480
Welcome back.

00:00:58.480 --> 00:01:00.690
I'm not late today.

00:00:58.590 --> 00:01:02.010
{\an9}Fuji Kiseki

00:01:01.700 --> 00:01:04.870
Your room's been decided,
so I just came to let you know.

00:01:04.870 --> 00:01:06.600
Your roommate is…

00:01:06.600 --> 00:01:07.570
Hmm?

00:01:07.570 --> 00:01:09.540
You already know each other?

00:01:09.540 --> 00:01:10.800
Huh?

00:01:12.820 --> 00:01:15.800
We're in the same room! It must be fate!

00:01:16.290 --> 00:01:18.230
Your things came.

00:01:18.230 --> 00:01:19.790
Thank you very much!

00:01:19.790 --> 00:01:21.100
Oh, I know.

00:01:21.770 --> 00:01:22.470
There.

00:01:22.470 --> 00:01:23.700
Hmm?

00:01:23.700 --> 00:01:25.590
I'm going to write my mom a letter.

00:01:25.590 --> 00:01:28.280
I'm going to tell her it was my first
time running with other horse girls.

00:01:28.280 --> 00:01:29.270
Your first time?

00:01:29.270 --> 00:01:32.260
And I'm going to tell her I got
to be in the same room as you,

00:01:32.260 --> 00:01:33.800
and that I joined a team!

00:01:33.800 --> 00:01:36.740
Oh, and that I have a debut race next week.

00:01:37.370 --> 00:01:39.050
I see…

00:01:39.050 --> 00:01:42.290
I don't know if I deserve
someone as great as you,

00:01:42.290 --> 00:01:43.720
but let's be friends!

00:01:44.630 --> 00:01:45.590
Sure.

00:01:53.770 --> 00:01:58.990
Do you hear the fanfare as
we race towards the finish?

00:01:58.990 --> 00:02:05.520
I want to see that shining future with you

00:02:07.560 --> 00:02:13.860
{\an8}Umamusume

00:02:09.440 --> 00:02:13.730
{\an8}Pretty Derby

00:02:15.750 --> 00:02:21.470
If we just start to run, that's
where our story will begin

00:02:21.470 --> 00:02:26.490
It's always waiting right in front of us

00:02:26.490 --> 00:02:32.100
If you reach out just a little
more, we can seize that glory

00:02:32.100 --> 00:02:38.960
Aim for the top, challenge
them all, and it's off to the races

00:02:39.770 --> 00:02:44.960
Even the goddess of victory will be dazzled

00:02:44.960 --> 00:02:52.240
By your big debut that's just around the bend

00:02:52.240 --> 00:02:57.660
So can you hear the fanfare
as we race towards the finish?

00:02:57.660 --> 00:03:03.130
I want to see that shining future with you

00:03:03.130 --> 00:03:08.640
Let's overtake them all! It's
a track laid out just for you!

00:03:08.640 --> 00:03:16.400
Your dreams are at the finish if you believe

00:03:17.960 --> 00:03:21.970
{\an8}Race 2
The Debut Race out of Nowhere

00:03:22.390 --> 00:03:25.180
All right! Let's race to that tree!

00:03:31.690 --> 00:03:33.230
Goal!

00:03:37.080 --> 00:03:38.320
One more race?

00:03:38.320 --> 00:03:39.690
Guess I have no choice.

00:03:39.690 --> 00:03:41.360
It's time to go.

00:03:41.360 --> 00:03:43.450
What?! The bird talked!

00:03:43.860 --> 00:03:45.410
Please hurry.

00:03:47.050 --> 00:03:47.930
Huh?

00:03:47.930 --> 00:03:49.500
You'll be late.

00:03:51.650 --> 00:03:54.210
What?! Oh no!

00:04:00.550 --> 00:04:04.010
Good morning.

00:04:04.010 --> 00:04:04.790
Hmm?

00:04:05.490 --> 00:04:06.600
Oh.

00:04:06.600 --> 00:04:09.170
Good morning, Special Week-san.

00:04:06.600 --> 00:04:09.620
{\an8}Hayakawa Tazuna

00:04:09.170 --> 00:04:10.670
Good morning!

00:04:10.670 --> 00:04:11.600
Hmm?

00:04:11.600 --> 00:04:15.380
{\an8}Class C

00:04:12.090 --> 00:04:15.380
This fill-in-the-blank problem is simple.

00:04:15.380 --> 00:04:20.360
Only Class C is allowed to participate
in the Satsuki Shou, Japan Derby, and what?

00:04:15.380 --> 00:04:20.360
{\an7}Only Class C is allowed to participate in the
Satsuki Shou, Japan Derby, and _________.

00:04:20.360 --> 00:04:22.180
Seiun Sky-san, please answer.

00:04:21.170 --> 00:04:24.410
{\an8}Seiun Sky

00:04:22.180 --> 00:04:23.610
The Kikkashou.

00:04:23.610 --> 00:04:24.410
That's correct.

00:04:24.790 --> 00:04:28.160
If you dominate these three G-I
races, you're honored as what?

00:04:28.160 --> 00:04:30.060
El Condor Pasa-san, please answer.

00:04:29.680 --> 00:04:33.040
{\an8}El Condor Pasa

00:04:30.060 --> 00:04:32.270
A Triple Crown Horse Girl!

00:04:32.270 --> 00:04:33.040
That's right.

00:04:33.040 --> 00:04:38.020
Recently, Mister CB, Symboli Rudolf,
Narita Brian,

00:04:38.020 --> 00:04:41.480
and others have proven their absolute
power and accomplished this.

00:04:41.480 --> 00:04:44.250
A-A Triple Crown Horse Girl…

00:04:47.210 --> 00:04:48.250
Special Week…

00:04:48.250 --> 00:04:49.100
Y-Yes?

00:04:49.140 --> 00:04:51.100
{\an7}Air Groove

00:04:49.630 --> 00:04:51.100
The Student Council President wants you.

00:04:52.390 --> 00:04:53.520
Huh?

00:04:53.520 --> 00:04:55.440
{\an8}Student Council President

00:04:55.880 --> 00:04:58.310
I am the student council president,
Symboli Rudolf.

00:04:56.000 --> 00:04:58.310
{\an8}Symboli Rudolf

00:04:59.330 --> 00:05:01.730
<i>She's a Triple Crown Horse Girl…</i>

00:05:01.730 --> 00:05:05.710
Our school is unique among horse girl
training facilities in that

00:05:05.710 --> 00:05:08.740
we have an impeccable and extensive
curriculum designed to cultivate

00:05:09.190 --> 00:05:12.260
elegant, superior horse girls.

00:05:12.260 --> 00:05:15.160
By applying oneself to their studies…

00:05:15.160 --> 00:05:19.320
{\an8}you will become upright and elegant, and…

00:05:15.570 --> 00:05:16.610
<i>What should I do…</i>

00:05:16.610 --> 00:05:19.320
<i>I only understand half
of what she's saying.</i>

00:05:19.910 --> 00:05:20.950
Special Week…

00:05:20.950 --> 00:05:21.880
Y-Yes!

00:05:22.340 --> 00:05:23.820
Are you listening?

00:05:23.820 --> 00:05:24.720
Yes.

00:05:25.490 --> 00:05:27.470
Where are you from?

00:05:27.470 --> 00:05:28.790
Hokkaido.

00:05:29.370 --> 00:05:30.330
I see.

00:05:31.330 --> 00:05:33.160
Your mother is…

00:05:33.160 --> 00:05:33.930
Yes.

00:05:34.260 --> 00:05:39.900
I promised my current mother that I would
become the best horse girl in Japan.

00:05:40.870 --> 00:05:43.650
It seems that you'll already be having
your debut match next week.

00:05:43.960 --> 00:05:46.250
Try your best to do well.

00:05:46.250 --> 00:05:47.990
Th-Thanks.

00:05:47.990 --> 00:05:50.740
Could you tell me how your debut race went?

00:05:51.080 --> 00:05:53.420
I had them under my thumb.

00:05:53.420 --> 00:05:55.660
<i>I guess that means she won?</i>

00:05:55.660 --> 00:05:57.300
You have a long future ahead of you.

00:05:57.300 --> 00:06:00.960
You should take a look at
the facilities we have here.

00:06:00.960 --> 00:06:04.550
Teio, don't hide back there. Come out.

00:06:04.550 --> 00:06:06.050
Hi!

00:06:06.520 --> 00:06:10.100
Special Week, this is Tokai Teio.

00:06:10.100 --> 00:06:11.430
N-Nice to meet you.

00:06:11.910 --> 00:06:15.030
Teio, show her the school.

00:06:12.990 --> 00:06:15.740
{\an8}Tokai Teio

00:06:15.030 --> 00:06:17.490
I'll do anything you say, Prez!

00:06:17.490 --> 00:06:18.440
Transfer Student, let's go!

00:06:18.910 --> 00:06:20.100
R-Right!

00:06:20.100 --> 00:06:21.970
Hold on, Special Week.

00:06:23.190 --> 00:06:25.110
Do you understand what this means?

00:06:27.480 --> 00:06:29.490
U-Uh…

00:06:29.930 --> 00:06:31.700
Eclip…

00:06:31.700 --> 00:06:34.210
It's the school motto.

00:06:34.790 --> 00:06:36.370
School motto?

00:06:36.370 --> 00:06:39.490
Sorry, I don't understand.

00:06:39.490 --> 00:06:40.250
I see.

00:06:40.870 --> 00:06:41.760
That's fine.

00:06:41.760 --> 00:06:42.880
Go take a look.

00:06:42.880 --> 00:06:43.730
Sure.

00:06:44.730 --> 00:06:46.710
U-Um, President…

00:06:46.710 --> 00:06:47.720
What is it?

00:06:48.200 --> 00:06:50.210
Thank you for everything.

00:06:56.870 --> 00:07:00.520
"Eclipse first, the rest nowhere."

00:07:00.520 --> 00:07:04.950
I'm sure there will come a time when
she understands what this means.

00:07:05.520 --> 00:07:07.530
{\an8}Library

00:07:06.230 --> 00:07:07.530
This is the library!

00:07:09.240 --> 00:07:11.860
Tracen Academy excels on
the track and in academics!

00:07:12.770 --> 00:07:14.080
There are so many books!

00:07:14.080 --> 00:07:15.160
Come over here!

00:07:16.410 --> 00:07:19.370
Could you guys be quiet?

00:07:16.850 --> 00:07:19.370
{\an8}Mejiro McQueen

00:07:19.720 --> 00:07:21.370
Sorry!

00:07:21.370 --> 00:07:23.880
This is the pool!

00:07:25.080 --> 00:07:27.750
It's my first time seeing a pool!

00:07:27.750 --> 00:07:29.740
Are there fish swimming…

00:07:29.740 --> 00:07:30.600
No.

00:07:30.600 --> 00:07:31.630
Yo!

00:07:33.490 --> 00:07:38.520
I could even beat fish
in short distance races!

00:07:35.950 --> 00:07:38.970
{\an7}Taiki Shuttle

00:07:40.920 --> 00:07:43.450
Feels so good!

00:07:44.350 --> 00:07:47.320
I'll show you around outside next!

00:07:47.320 --> 00:07:51.000
Darn it! I lost again!

00:07:47.320 --> 00:07:48.900
{\an8}Hishi Amazon

00:07:50.130 --> 00:07:51.400
{\an7}Narita Brian

00:07:51.000 --> 00:07:53.160
Why?! Come on!

00:07:53.480 --> 00:07:54.330
What's that about?

00:07:54.330 --> 00:07:56.100
I'm sure she feels bad she lost.

00:07:55.870 --> 00:07:58.660
{\an8}I'm going to win next time!

00:07:56.100 --> 00:07:58.660
She's letting out her feelings there.

00:07:58.970 --> 00:08:01.590
Next time!

00:08:01.590 --> 00:08:02.710
Oh, yeah.

00:08:03.110 --> 00:08:05.950
Are you trying to become
a Triple Crown Horse Girl?

00:08:05.950 --> 00:08:09.130
Well, I don't have any
specific races in mind.

00:08:09.130 --> 00:08:10.990
You have no specific goals?

00:08:10.990 --> 00:08:12.590
I guess.

00:08:12.590 --> 00:08:15.070
So, what did you think of the President?

00:08:15.070 --> 00:08:17.010
Symboli Rudolf-san?

00:08:17.010 --> 00:08:20.180
The president runs really fast!
She's really cool!

00:08:20.180 --> 00:08:21.970
She's the best!

00:08:22.470 --> 00:08:25.690
You love the President, huh, Teio-san?

00:08:25.690 --> 00:08:26.480
Yeah!

00:08:26.970 --> 00:08:30.360
I want to be like the President.

00:08:30.360 --> 00:08:33.430
She's called the Emperor.

00:08:33.430 --> 00:08:35.310
It's my dream to be like her.

00:08:35.310 --> 00:08:36.660
It's my goal.

00:08:38.570 --> 00:08:40.230
She knows exactly what she wants.

00:08:41.880 --> 00:08:43.830
<i>My goal is…</i>

00:08:50.120 --> 00:08:50.850
<i>All right!</i>

00:08:50.850 --> 00:08:52.640
<i>I have my debut race!</i>

00:08:52.640 --> 00:08:54.930
<i>I have to work hard during
my first training session!</i>

00:08:55.320 --> 00:08:57.250
Next. Right hand, blue.

00:08:59.220 --> 00:09:01.720
That's great, Special Week!

00:09:01.720 --> 00:09:04.110
What's up with this training?

00:09:04.110 --> 00:09:06.260
I want to do this, too! Okay?!

00:09:06.260 --> 00:09:08.470
There's no point to this, is there?

00:09:08.470 --> 00:09:09.570
There is!

00:09:09.570 --> 00:09:11.580
Then explain it!

00:09:11.580 --> 00:09:12.680
Special Week.

00:09:12.680 --> 00:09:13.740
Y-Yes?!

00:09:13.740 --> 00:09:17.530
Your debut race is different from
the team test you had yesterday.

00:09:17.530 --> 00:09:19.660
You should think of races as martial arts.

00:09:19.660 --> 00:09:22.360
Your opponents will come and bump you.

00:09:22.360 --> 00:09:26.500
You'll have to strengthen your core muscles,
so you don't lose your balance.

00:09:26.950 --> 00:09:29.080
Yeah, but how will this game help?

00:09:30.310 --> 00:09:31.810
El, focus!

00:09:32.360 --> 00:09:34.680
This is embarrassing!

00:09:34.680 --> 00:09:37.840
{\an8}Mom, I'm working hard for my debut race!

00:09:38.970 --> 00:09:42.970
{\an8}Uma<font color="#fbc1bb">musume</font>

00:09:38.970 --> 00:09:42.970
{\an8}Pretty Derby

00:09:44.100 --> 00:09:45.930
Good morning, Spe-chan!

00:09:45.930 --> 00:09:48.650
You'll be Bracket 8, Number 14
for your debut race!

00:09:45.930 --> 00:09:48.650
{\an7}Special Week Queen-Berry Soft Seikou
Kuuruma Kaberune Stella Hunt Kizunawan

00:09:48.650 --> 00:09:50.200
Clockwise…

00:09:50.200 --> 00:09:51.690
One thousand, six hundred meters…

00:09:51.690 --> 00:09:52.820
Turf, huh?

00:09:52.820 --> 00:09:55.280
Wow, wow, wow!

00:09:55.280 --> 00:09:57.240
That's so great!

00:09:59.000 --> 00:10:05.074
Do you want subtitles for any video?
-=[ ai.OpenSubtitles.com ]=-

00:10:35.530 --> 00:10:37.880
Suzuka, do you have a moment?

00:10:37.880 --> 00:10:38.570
Yes?

00:10:41.170 --> 00:10:44.280
I'd like you to do something
for Special Week.

00:10:45.130 --> 00:10:48.520
She's a bit unique, it seems.

00:10:49.670 --> 00:10:52.890
I want you to look after
her here in the dorms.

00:10:52.890 --> 00:10:54.000
Unique?

00:10:54.740 --> 00:11:00.300
She hadn't ever met another
horse girl before now.

00:11:00.300 --> 00:11:03.050
Huh? But her mom would…

00:11:04.420 --> 00:11:07.720
I don't know the details myself, either.

00:11:08.730 --> 00:11:11.320
I just know she was raised in the countryside

00:11:11.320 --> 00:11:14.690
without any other kids her age
or any other horse girls around.

00:11:14.690 --> 00:11:17.620
She couldn't really make friends, it seems.

00:11:18.320 --> 00:11:21.230
On top of that, she has
her debut race tomorrow.

00:11:21.230 --> 00:11:24.910
She might seem cheerful, but I'm sure some
things are hard for her to say, as well.

00:11:24.910 --> 00:11:28.200
Could you stay by her side,
since you're her roommate?

00:11:29.730 --> 00:11:31.120
Sure.

00:11:39.510 --> 00:11:41.510
{\an8}Mom

00:11:42.490 --> 00:11:43.570
<i>Her letter…</i>

00:11:44.640 --> 00:11:46.360
You start here,

00:11:44.640 --> 00:11:48.850
{\an7}Start

00:11:46.360 --> 00:11:47.820
go around the corner,

00:11:47.820 --> 00:11:48.850
and finish here.

00:11:49.290 --> 00:11:50.680
R-Right.

00:11:50.680 --> 00:11:53.020
So what should Spe-senpai's plan be?

00:11:53.020 --> 00:11:55.020
She should make a dash
from the start, obviously.

00:11:55.020 --> 00:11:57.400
She should force herself
into the inside corner.

00:11:57.400 --> 00:11:59.560
Nope! No plans at all!

00:11:59.560 --> 00:12:00.530
What?!

00:12:00.870 --> 00:12:02.240
No plans?!

00:12:03.030 --> 00:12:04.280
{\an8}Debut Race

00:12:03.030 --> 00:12:04.280
{\an8}Start

00:12:03.030 --> 00:12:04.280
{\an8}Goal

00:12:05.540 --> 00:12:07.270
The plan is no plan?

00:12:07.270 --> 00:12:08.450
Yeah, that's it…

00:12:08.450 --> 00:12:11.830
{\an8}Debut Race

00:12:08.450 --> 00:12:11.830
{\an8}Start

00:12:11.830 --> 00:12:17.540
{\an6}Debut Race

00:12:11.830 --> 00:12:17.540
{\an6}Start

00:12:12.500 --> 00:12:13.770
Special Week.

00:12:13.770 --> 00:12:15.830
Don't think of trying to
come up with a strategy.

00:12:15.830 --> 00:12:17.540
Run the way you want.

00:12:17.540 --> 00:12:19.010
The way I want…

00:12:19.010 --> 00:12:22.050
It can be at the start or the finish,
or whenever you want…

00:12:22.050 --> 00:12:26.550
You can start your sprint whenever you
feel it's the right time for you.

00:12:23.550 --> 00:12:26.550
{\an6}Debut Race

00:12:23.550 --> 00:12:26.550
{\an6}Start

00:12:26.550 --> 00:12:28.970
Pass the horse girl in the lead.

00:12:29.940 --> 00:12:31.980
I wonder if I'll know the right time.

00:12:31.980 --> 00:12:35.690
Part of it is experience,
and part of it is gut instinct.

00:12:35.690 --> 00:12:37.850
You'll just have to give it a shot.

00:12:51.240 --> 00:12:54.710
Could you stay by her side,
since you're her roommate?

00:12:57.890 --> 00:12:59.670
Are you worried about something?

00:13:01.400 --> 00:13:02.920
Oh, I'm sorry.

00:13:02.920 --> 00:13:05.840
I shouldn't sigh.

00:13:05.840 --> 00:13:07.480
Special Week-san…

00:13:07.480 --> 00:13:08.090
Yes?

00:13:10.310 --> 00:13:11.580
When you joined our team,

00:13:11.580 --> 00:13:14.520
you said you wanted to be the
best horse girl in Japan, right?

00:13:14.930 --> 00:13:16.410
Oh, yeah.

00:13:16.410 --> 00:13:18.530
Why the best in Japan?

00:13:20.230 --> 00:13:23.420
Because that's what I promised my mom.

00:13:23.420 --> 00:13:24.650
Your mom…

00:13:25.050 --> 00:13:28.660
Suzuka-san, I have two mothers.

00:13:30.160 --> 00:13:33.130
One of them is the mom
that gave birth to me.

00:13:33.650 --> 00:13:36.600
She died giving birth to me.

00:13:41.090 --> 00:13:42.380
Please make her…

00:13:43.560 --> 00:13:45.990
Make her a wonderful horse girl…

00:13:46.630 --> 00:13:49.140
Those were her dying words.

00:13:50.580 --> 00:13:54.100
My second mother wanted to be
faithful to those dying words.

00:13:54.100 --> 00:13:56.390
She tried her best to raise me.

00:13:55.370 --> 00:13:59.100
{\an8}You can do it!

00:13:58.070 --> 00:14:02.690
She did whatever she could to help me.

00:14:02.690 --> 00:14:05.690
{\an8}Come on! You can go faster!

00:14:03.650 --> 00:14:06.280
When it was even raining, windy, or snowing,

00:14:06.280 --> 00:14:09.390
she'd help me train in the countryside,
even with no proper facilities.

00:14:09.390 --> 00:14:11.700
Take that! Take that!

00:14:15.860 --> 00:14:18.570
What was that training for?

00:14:18.570 --> 00:14:19.660
Um…

00:14:19.660 --> 00:14:20.980
I don't know.

00:14:22.630 --> 00:14:26.650
If she helped raise me to
be Japan's best horse girl,

00:14:26.650 --> 00:14:31.430
then my mom that raised me will have
kept her promise to my mom that died.

00:14:31.430 --> 00:14:35.600
She even brought a sign when she saw
me off at the train station.

00:14:33.810 --> 00:14:35.740
{\an8}Become the Best in Japan, Special Week

00:14:39.170 --> 00:14:41.480
That's so embarrassing…

00:14:41.800 --> 00:14:44.170
That's why I want to be the best in Japan.

00:14:44.170 --> 00:14:46.070
I have to make it up to both my moms!

00:14:48.790 --> 00:14:51.990
It's nice that you have two moms.

00:14:51.990 --> 00:14:53.130
Yeah!

00:14:58.620 --> 00:15:03.960
Sunday Pillow, who was supposed to run
in today's main race, has withdrawn.

00:15:03.960 --> 00:15:05.300
That's right.

00:15:08.200 --> 00:15:11.580
It's time to watch Spe's debut race.

00:15:11.580 --> 00:15:13.450
It's unfair that she's going before me.

00:15:13.450 --> 00:15:16.850
I forgot to tell her how to
show herself on the paddock.

00:15:17.160 --> 00:15:19.350
Next, we have Bracket 8, Number 14,

00:15:20.150 --> 00:15:21.610
Special Week.

00:15:27.450 --> 00:15:31.180
<i>She's pretty stiff out there.</i>

00:15:31.180 --> 00:15:33.060
<i>Well, I guess it's her debut race.</i>

00:15:33.060 --> 00:15:35.700
<i>It makes sense that she'd be nervous.</i>

00:15:36.930 --> 00:15:39.540
She's moving her arms and feet together!

00:15:47.300 --> 00:15:50.050
She's way too nervous.

00:15:51.140 --> 00:15:54.510
Oh, I forgot to give her the bib.

00:15:54.510 --> 00:15:56.440
That's an issue.

00:15:56.440 --> 00:15:58.260
Come on, now.

00:15:58.580 --> 00:15:59.720
Suzuka…

00:15:59.720 --> 00:16:00.570
Hmm?

00:16:01.140 --> 00:16:05.020
Could you take this to Special Week?

00:16:05.020 --> 00:16:06.010
Okay.

00:16:22.500 --> 00:16:24.610
Suzuka-san, why are you here?

00:16:25.090 --> 00:16:26.040
I brought this.

00:16:27.930 --> 00:16:28.750
There you are.

00:16:28.750 --> 00:16:30.300
Thank you very much.

00:16:31.030 --> 00:16:33.220
You're nervous, huh?

00:16:33.220 --> 00:16:37.300
It's my first time being
in front of so many people.

00:16:37.640 --> 00:16:41.230
It's all about thinking whether
the pressure is scary or fun.

00:16:41.230 --> 00:16:41.890
Huh?

00:16:42.310 --> 00:16:46.990
It's your first step toward the goal
you set with both of your mothers.

00:16:46.990 --> 00:16:48.860
It'd be a shame if you were just scared.

00:16:51.290 --> 00:16:52.790
You have to have fun,

00:16:53.380 --> 00:16:54.250
Spe…

00:16:55.530 --> 00:16:56.570
Spe-chan!

00:16:57.940 --> 00:16:59.300
Suzuka-san…

00:16:59.940 --> 00:17:00.970
You're right!

00:17:17.300 --> 00:17:19.250
That girl looks kind of good!

00:17:19.250 --> 00:17:20.960
Who's #14, again?

00:17:20.960 --> 00:17:22.770
You can do it, Special Week!

00:17:24.010 --> 00:17:26.000
Hey…

00:17:26.000 --> 00:17:28.730
She's acting completely
different than she was before.

00:17:35.770 --> 00:17:37.540
<i>It'd be a shame if I was just scared.</i>

00:17:37.540 --> 00:17:39.130
<i>I have to have fun.</i>

00:17:39.130 --> 00:17:40.180
All right!

00:17:40.180 --> 00:17:41.950
What's "all right"?

00:17:42.520 --> 00:17:43.620
I'll crush you!

00:17:43.620 --> 00:17:45.290
What?!

00:17:46.180 --> 00:17:47.960
<i>They've all taken off together.</i>

00:17:47.960 --> 00:17:50.250
<i>Actually, they're off of
the line a bit broken up.</i>

00:17:50.250 --> 00:17:55.370
<i>Number 9, Sara Poole, and Number 4,
Victory Wild, are fighting for first!</i>

00:17:55.370 --> 00:17:58.560
<i>And Number 2, Last Century,
is coming up from the inside!</i>

00:17:58.560 --> 00:18:03.220
<i>Oh! Number 14, Special Week, who was
late off the line, is in fifth!</i>

00:18:03.220 --> 00:18:05.670
Spe-senpai is heading up
the front of the pack.

00:18:05.670 --> 00:18:07.140
<i>Don't think about anything.</i>

00:18:07.140 --> 00:18:10.060
<i>You're not experienced enough
to think about strategy.</i>

00:18:13.530 --> 00:18:16.680
Here I come!

00:18:18.390 --> 00:18:20.490
Queen-Berry is testing the waters.

00:18:20.490 --> 00:18:22.910
Is she going to come fighting?

00:18:23.220 --> 00:18:24.450
Out of the way!

00:18:26.370 --> 00:18:28.330
<i>She's running strong.</i>

00:18:28.720 --> 00:18:31.040
She's got a lot of power.

00:18:31.040 --> 00:18:33.550
She hasn't lost a single match
at arm wrestling, supposedly.

00:18:36.050 --> 00:18:37.640
<i>They've passed the third corner.</i>

00:18:37.640 --> 00:18:39.050
<i>There's 600 meters left.</i>

00:18:44.120 --> 00:18:45.060
Darn.

00:18:49.560 --> 00:18:51.470
She's doing good.

00:18:51.470 --> 00:18:54.070
Her mom's training helped.

00:18:54.070 --> 00:18:55.570
Her mom?

00:18:57.570 --> 00:18:59.100
<i>They're making the fourth turn.</i>

00:18:59.100 --> 00:19:00.820
<i>There's 400 meters left.</i>

00:19:03.990 --> 00:19:06.360
<i>Queen-Berry has made her move!</i>

00:19:06.360 --> 00:19:08.750
<i>She's jumped into first!</i>

00:19:15.370 --> 00:19:16.370
<i>This is it.</i>

00:19:26.390 --> 00:19:27.890
<i>Yep, that's it.</i>

00:19:27.890 --> 00:19:30.440
No way!

00:19:33.620 --> 00:19:34.690
<i>I can do this!</i>

00:19:35.830 --> 00:19:37.650
<i>Wh-What?</i>

00:19:54.370 --> 00:19:55.530
<i>I'm going to win!</i>

00:19:55.530 --> 00:19:58.250
<i>I can't lose now!</i>

00:20:01.530 --> 00:20:02.510
<i>This can't be!</i>

00:20:27.120 --> 00:20:29.030
Special Week!

00:20:29.030 --> 00:20:30.450
Yeah!

00:20:44.520 --> 00:20:46.950
{\an8}Special Week has won!

00:20:46.950 --> 00:20:48.940
{\an8}She's won her debut race!

00:20:48.940 --> 00:20:51.090
{\an8}Has a new star been born?

00:20:48.940 --> 00:20:51.090
<i>Mom, I've done it!</i>

00:20:53.220 --> 00:20:54.830
She's good.

00:20:54.830 --> 00:20:57.690
Hey! Give me my debut race, too!

00:20:57.690 --> 00:20:59.150
I'm first, right?!

00:20:59.150 --> 00:21:00.480
I know, I know.

00:21:00.890 --> 00:21:03.580
Let's keep this up and
have Team Spica take over!

00:21:03.580 --> 00:21:04.680
Yeah!

00:21:10.810 --> 00:21:12.140
Looks like you're having fun.

00:21:12.140 --> 00:21:14.960
That girl at the end's a diamond
in the rough, you know?

00:21:15.350 --> 00:21:17.710
Hana-san, you can't pick 'em.

00:21:17.710 --> 00:21:19.870
All she did is win her debut race.

00:21:19.870 --> 00:21:23.110
You want to bet on whether she remains
in the rough, or becomes a diamond?

00:21:23.750 --> 00:21:24.970
Ridiculous.

00:21:26.150 --> 00:21:30.690
Above all, make sure you
hold Silence Suzuka's reins tight.

00:21:34.710 --> 00:21:38.810
<i>Now it's time for the Winning Concert,
where only the winners gets to stand.</i>

00:21:38.810 --> 00:21:39.600
<i>That's right.</i>

00:21:38.810 --> 00:21:41.570
{\an8}Horse Girls in 1st, 2nd, and 3rd, come
this way. (Winning Concert Green Room)

00:21:39.600 --> 00:21:44.790
<i>it'll be Special Week's
first performance on stage.</i>

00:21:42.210 --> 00:21:44.790
{\an8}Winning Concert…

00:21:57.880 --> 00:21:59.460
Oh, crap.

00:21:59.460 --> 00:22:03.240
We didn't practice how to handle
the Winning Stage at all.

00:22:03.240 --> 00:22:04.090
Huh?

00:22:10.570 --> 00:22:11.600
Come on, now.

00:22:12.090 --> 00:22:13.300
Oh no.

00:22:14.330 --> 00:22:16.200
She's funny!

00:22:19.480 --> 00:22:24.940
<i>Mom, I didn't practice dancing at all…</i>

00:22:25.650 --> 00:22:28.720
In a dash, in a flash,
just a little more now,

00:22:28.720 --> 00:22:31.430
each new race like a dream neverending

00:22:31.430 --> 00:22:34.240
Every one of us will blaze a
trail aimed right for the stars

00:22:34.240 --> 00:22:39.410
Together we'll run! Let's
go! Our starting gate!

00:22:48.540 --> 00:22:53.870
With curiosity in hand, go tug
on tomorrow's tail and say hello

00:22:53.870 --> 00:22:58.870
It's right there, so go on and close
the gap now (Right here and now!)

00:22:59.580 --> 00:23:04.960
Can't play by the rules they tell
you! Gotta learn it all by experience!

00:23:04.960 --> 00:23:09.900
If we just plan to run for the
end, everything will turn out okay!

00:23:10.060 --> 00:23:13.930
Can't get me down,
hesitate, or go too slowly!

00:23:15.680 --> 00:23:19.650
We know that deep in our hearts is a song

00:23:19.730 --> 00:23:22.870
that sings "give it your all"! Make it shine!

00:23:23.450 --> 00:23:26.670
In a dash, in a flash, just a
little more now, (Dash! Dash!)

00:23:26.670 --> 00:23:29.420
every step like the wind
neverending (Zoom! Zoom!)

00:23:29.420 --> 00:23:32.320
A twinkling star that we wear
on our sleeves (But only one!)

00:23:32.320 --> 00:23:34.620
Let's let our hearts race
together as one! (Grow up! Shine!)

00:23:34.620 --> 00:23:37.750
One more step, one more push,
just a little more now, (Dash! Dash!)

00:23:37.750 --> 00:23:40.400
each new race like a dream
neverending (Zoom! Zoom!)

00:23:40.400 --> 00:23:43.250
Every one of us will see
our path to the very end!

00:23:43.250 --> 00:23:48.980
Let's run now, everyone!
Let's go! Our starting gate!

00:23:49.305 --> 00:24:49.805
